1. *Leti* se po nebu avion. (The plane is flying in the sky.)
2. *Lete* ptice prema jugu. (The birds are flying south.)
3. On je *leteo* u zemlju. (He flew to the ground.)
4. Šta će on *leteti*? (What will he fly?)
5. Njeni sanovi su joj *letele* po glavi. (Her dreams were flying through her head.)
6. Ona je *letela* na letelici. (She was flying on a kite.)
7. *Leti* li on u Pariz? (Is he flying to Paris?)
8. Da li će *leteti* do Beograda? (Will they fly to Belgrade?)